            "value": "<p><em>You command a creature to submit to your power, and as you worm your way into they mind, you bend a small piece of iron. As you do, your target feels as if they are unable to move more than slightly, as if chained by invisible chains.</em></p><p dir=\"auto\" id=\"viewer-alid55200\"><span><strong>Wisdom Save</strong> </span></p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"auto\"><p id=\"viewer-8kive5201\"><span><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[Restrained]. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</span></p></li><li aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"auto\"><p id=\"viewer-jb47s613\"><span><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</span></p></li></ul><p dir=\"auto\" id=\"viewer-iysav5204\"><span>*<strong>Upcasting</strong> : Target one additional creature for each spell level above 2nd.</span></p>",
